%% Full sequence: nurse request -> station scan -> private result back to nurse iPad

sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Nurse as Nurse iPad<br/>apps/nurse-webapp
  participant Backend as Backend<br/>apps/backend
  participant Kafka as Kafka
  participant Station as Station Display<br/>apps/station-display
  participant Reader as Reader Agent<br/>apps/reader-agent
  participant Card as Thai ID Card Reader

  Nurse->>Backend: SSE /api/stations/A01/status/events<br/>safe readiness only
  Reader->>Kafka: produce reader.status.A01<br/>heartbeat, readerReady
  Kafka-->>Backend: consume reader heartbeat
  Backend-->>Nurse: SSE readiness<br/>ready/busy/offline, queue depth
  Backend-->>Station: SSE readiness<br/>reader freshness, safe timing

  Nurse->>Backend: POST /api/scan-requests<br/>nurseId, stationId, deviceSessionId
  Backend->>Backend: Create requestId, deviceSessionId,<br/>5-char turnCode, queue state

  alt reader offline
    Backend->>Backend: Queue or pause request creation<br/>no active scan timer
    Backend-->>Nurse: readiness says reader offline<br/>private result SSE not opened yet
  else station is neutral and reader ready
    Backend->>Backend: Activate request<br/>set activatedAt and expiresAt
    Backend->>Kafka: produce scan.requests<br/>active request, no card PII
    Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>turnCode/status/queueDepth only
    Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>active + turnCode
    Kafka-->>Reader: consume scan.requests
    Reader->>Reader: Track active requestId
    Reader->>Kafka: produce reader.status.A01<br/>waiting_for_card
    Kafka-->>Backend: consume reader.status.A01
    Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>reader waiting_for_card
  else station busy or cooldown
    Backend->>Backend: Queue request<br/>no expiresAt yet
    Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>queueDepth update
    Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>queued/queueDepth
    Backend-->>Nurse: 201 queued<br/>turnCode, queuePosition
  end

  Backend-->>Nurse: 201 active/queued<br/>requestId, deviceSessionId, turnCode
  Nurse->>Backend: SSE /api/scan-results/{deviceSessionId}/events

  Nurse->>Nurse: Compare iPad code with station code
  Card->>Reader: Card inserted and read
  Reader->>Kafka: produce reader.status.A01<br/>reading
  Reader->>Kafka: produce reader.card-read<br/>requestId + card payload

  alt retryable read failure
    Reader->>Kafka: produce reader.status.A01<br/>read_failed_retryable
    Kafka-->>Backend: consume retryable reader status
    Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>Read failed, reinsert card
    Backend-->>Nurse: SSE request-status<br/>retryable_error, same turnCode
    Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>Read failed - reinsert card
  else read succeeds
  Kafka-->>Backend: consume reader.card-read
  Backend->>Backend: Validate active requestId<br/>lookup deviceSessionId
  Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>reading
  Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>reading
  Backend->>Kafka: produce scan-result.{deviceSessionId}<br/>full card payload + photo
  Backend-->>Nurse: SSE scan-result<br/>private card payload + photo
  Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>delivered
  Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>delivered
  Backend->>Kafka: produce audit.scan-events<br/>card_scan_received/result_delivered
  Backend-->>Nurse: SSE request-status later<br/>result_clear_recommended

  Backend->>Backend: Start 3s cooldown
  Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>cooldown + cooldownUntil
  Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>cooldown countdown
  Backend-->>Reader: via station.status.A01<br/>clear active request

  alt queued request exists after cooldown
    Backend->>Backend: Activate next queued request<br/>fresh expiresAt starts now
    Backend->>Kafka: produce scan.requests<br/>next active request
    Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>next turnCode
    Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>next active code
    Kafka-->>Reader: consume next scan.requests
  else no queued request
    Backend->>Kafka: produce station.status.A01<br/>neutral
    Backend-->>Station: SSE station-status<br/>neutral/ready
  end
  end

  Note over Station: Station display must never show citizen ID,<br/>patient name, address, photo, or raw card data.
  Note over Nurse,Backend: 5-char turnCode is human confirmation only.<br/>Backend routes private data by requestId + deviceSessionId.
  Note over Nurse,Backend: NurseID/device auth hardening is deferred<br/>until hospital authentication rules are known.
